beer.beer_description:
Style - A Kveik brewed West Coast IPA. This bay boy is 6.2% Hoppy AF and heaps drinkable. We use 7(Yes Seven!) different hops and we've chucked them into a really black can. Cool eh?!
-HOPS: Topaz, Cascade, Centennial, Columbus, Simco, Chinook, Amarillo
-ABV: 6.2%
-CAN: Superblack.... supercool.....
